<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recruitment Request Creation Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                <!-- Main container -->
                <table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                    <!-- Confidential bar -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 8px 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; text-align: right; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
                            CONFIDENTIAL - FOR INTERNAL USE ONLY
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    
                    <!-- Title bar -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #D4AF37; color: #fff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; position: relative;">
                            <!-- Document seal as embeddable image - Giải pháp 1: Sử dụng base64 cho SVG -->
                            <div style="position: absolute; right: 10px; top: 10px; width: 120px; height: 120px; opacity: 0.2;">
                                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="DENSO seal" width="120" height="120" style="opacity: 0.2;">
                            </div>
                            
                            <h2 style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;">RECRUITMENT REQUEST CREATION NOTIFICATION</h2>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    
                    <!-- Content -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 30px 20px; position: relative;">
                            <!-- Confidential watermark - Giải pháp sử dụng background image -->
                            <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1;">
                                <table width="100%" height="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td align="center" valign="middle">
                                            <div style="font-size: 80px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); font-weight: bold; transform: rotate(-45deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(-45deg); -ms-transform: rotate(-45deg);">CONFIDENTIAL</div>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Actual content in a separate table to ensure it's on top of the watermark -->
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
                                        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #D4AF37; margin: 10px 0;"></div>
                                        <p>The system would like to inform you that your recruitment request has been successfully created with the following details:</p>
                                        
                                        <!-- Info table -->
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin: 25px 0; border-color: #ddd;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <th style="padding: 12px; background-color: #f8f4e5; width: 40%; color: #333; text-align: left;">Request Creator:</th>
                                                <td style="padding: 12px;">[Creator Name]</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th style="padding: 12px; background-color: #f8f4e5; width: 40%; color: #333; text-align: left;">Recruitment Request ID:</th>
                                                <td style="padding: 12px;">[Request ID]</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th style="padding: 12px; background-color: #f8f4e5; width: 40%; color: #333; text-align: left;">Position:</th>
                                                <td style="padding: 12px;">[Position Name]</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th style="padding: 12px; background-color: #f8f4e5; width: 40%; color: #333; text-align: left;">Creation Time:</th>
                                                <td style="padding: 12px;">[Day/Month/Year - Hour:Minute]</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th style="padding: 12px; background-color: #f8f4e5; width: 40%; color: #333; text-align: left;">Status:</th>
                                                <td style="padding: 12px;">Pending Approval</td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                        
                                        <p>To track the progress of your recruitment request, please click on the link below:</p>
                                        
                                        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                                            <a href="[Progress tracking link]" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #D4AF37; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">Track Progress</a>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <div style="background-color: #f8f4e5; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #D4AF37; margin-top: 25px;">
                                            <strong>Note:</strong> This is an automated email sent from the system. Please do not reply to this email.
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    
                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 15px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 12px; color: #666; background-color: #f5f5f5;">
                            <p style="margin: 5px 0;">© 2025 DENSO MANUFACTURING VIETNAM CO.,LTD. All rights reserved.</p>
                            <p style="margin: 5px 0;">This email was sent from the recruitment management system of DENSO MANUFACTURING VIETNAM CO.,LTD.</p>
                            <p style="margin: 5px 0;">The information in this email may be confidential and is intended only for the designated recipient.</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>